__NAME__ purpose
specify name of a database to use with DBI-based sessions
__END__


__NAME__ synopsis
<arg choice='plain'><replaceable>database_name</replaceable></arg>
__END__


__NAME__ see also
SessionType,SessionDatabase,SessionDB, SessionExpire,SessionLockFile
__END__


__NAME__ description
The directive specifies the name of a database to be used with
DBI-based user &glos-session;s.
__END__

__NAME__ notes
Using this directive (DBI sessions in general) is not recommended.
__END__

__NAME__ example: Setting SessionDB
Put the following in &ccf;:
<programlisting>
SessionDB sessions
</programlisting>
__END__



__NAME__ missing
Why DBI sessions are not encouraged?
__END__
